name: AVAssetExportSession
desc: An object that transcodes the contents of an asset source object to create an output of the form described by a specified export preset.

items.name: outputURL
items.desc: The URL of the export sessionâ€™s output.

items.name: supportedFileTypes
items.desc: An array containing the types of files the session can write.

items.name: outputFileType
items.desc: The type of file written by the session.

items.name: fileLengthLimit
items.desc: The file length that the output of the session should not exceed.

items.name: timeRange
items.desc: The time range exported from the source.

items.name: metadata
items.desc: The metadata written to the output file by the export session.

items.name: metadataItemFilter
items.desc: Specifies a filter object used during export to determine which metadata items to transfer from the source asset.

items.name: audioMix
items.desc: The parameters for audio mixing and an indication whether to enable nondefault audio mixing for export.

items.name: audioTimePitchAlgorithm
items.desc: A processing algorithm used to manage audio pitch for scaled audio edits.

items.name: shouldOptimizeForNetworkUse
items.desc: A Boolean value that indicates whether to optimize the movie should for network use.

items.name: videoComposition
items.desc: The instructions for video composition, and indicates whether video composition is enabled for export.

items.name: customVideoCompositor
items.desc: The custom video compositor instance used, if any.

items.name: canPerformMultiplePassesOverSourceMediaData
items.desc: A Boolean value that indicates whether the export session can perform multiple passes over the source media to achieve better results.

items.name: directoryForTemporaryFiles
items.desc: A directory that is suitable for containing temporary files generated during the export process.

items.name: presetName
items.desc: The name of the preset used to initialize the session.

items.name: allExportPresets
items.desc: Returns all available export preset names.

items.name: exportPresets
items.desc: Returns the identifiers compatible with a given asset.

items.name: cancelExport
items.desc: Cancels the execution of an export session.

items.name: error
items.desc: Describes the error that occurred.

items.name: AVAssetExportSession.Status
items.desc: A set of statuses used for relaying the state of an export session.

items.name: estimatedOutputFileLength
items.desc: The estimated size, in bytes, of the exported file.

items.name: maxDuration
items.desc: Provides an estimate of the maximum duration of the exported media.

items.name: progress
items.desc: The progress of the export on a scale from 0 to 1.

items.name: status
items.desc: The status of the export session.

items.name: asset
items.desc: The asset used to initialize the export session.

items.name: AVVideoTransferFunction_ITU_R_2100_HLG
items.desc: The transfer function for the ITU_R BT.2100 color space.
